Package GUI

package GUI
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    GameGUI
    This Graphical User Interface Launches the game for the player to play By RMI service the email of the current player is retrived from LoginGUI to assign the score of the player
    GameInstructionGUI
    This Graphical user interface lauches the instuction of the game for the player read and understand about the game
    LoginGUI
    This Graphical user interface launches the login display for player to enter the player's credentials to gain access to play the game.
    MainMenuGUI
    This Graphical user interface is the MainMenu of the Game where the player can navigate other GUIs and services
    RegisterGUI
    This Graphical user interface launches the registation display for player to enter player's details.
    ScoreBoardGUI
    This Graphical user interface launches the scoreboard of the game where each player's name and score is displayed if the player is registed and not played the score cell will show blank.
